  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM6.6.7">
<l>mulaittaṭatta nañcuṇṭu tuñcap pēycci mututuvaraik kulapatiyāk kālip piṉṉē</l>
<l>yilaittaṭatta kuḻalūti yāyar māta riṉavaḷaikoṇ ṭāṉaṭikkī ḻeyta kiṟpīr</l>
<l>malaittaṭatta maṇikoṇarntu vaiya muyya vaḷaṅkoṭukkum varupuṉalam poṉṉi nāṭaṉ</l>
<l>cilaittaṭakkaik kulaccōḻaṉ cērnta kōyil tirunaṟaiyūr maṇimāṭañ cērmiṉ kaḷē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You who are able to approach low at the feet of the one who took</l>
<l rend="indent">various bangles from herder women, having blown a flute</l>
<l rend="indent">from a broad leaf [following] behind the herd,</l>
<l>Becoming the clan leader of ancient Dwaraka, having eaten poison</l>
<l rend="indent">from the broad breasts of the demoness so that she perished,</l>
<l>Gather at the beautiful raised shrine in Tirunaṟaiyūr, the temple where came</l>
<l rend="indent">the one of the Cōḻa clan, a bow in [his] broad hand,</l>
<l>Lord of the lovely Poṉṉi [River] land with floods that rise,</l>
<l rend="indent">[and] provide prosperity so the earth thrives,</l>
<l rend="indent">bringing jewels from broad mountains.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
